title: 6 Books & Magazines (gnv64)
description:
This torrent contains 4 books & 2 magazines:

1.  Anatomy for Runners: Unlocking Your Athletic Potential for Health, Speed, and Injury Prevention by Jay Dicharry (Aug 1, 2012) 
2. Biomimetics - A Molecular Perspective (De Gruyter Textbook) by Raz Jelinek (May 1, 2013)
3.  Complete Electronics Self-Teaching Guide with Projects by Earl Boysen and Harry Kybett (Jul 31, 2012) 
4.  The Science Delusion: Asking the Big Questions in a Culture of Easy Answers by Curtis White (May 28, 2013) 
5. First Glimpse - July 2013
6. GeoIntelligence - May/June 2013
